    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hello, \n\nIf you are not using the builded version of instantsearch.js (jsDelivr) then you need to build your project using webpack's ENV plugin: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/9aa93e0d7ae9843729f158c8deff679eaf8ec7d2/scripts/webpack.config.jsdelivr.babel.js#L29-L35\n\nThen on the command line, when building: `NODE_ENV=production npm run build`\n",
